                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a cabinet-maker. I matched the lead with the last witness, at Mr. Serjeant's, in Queen-street; these are only a part of the whole that was taken, which was seventy foot; but two of these pieces match.</p>
               <p>
            
