               <p>It was my house at that time; I matched this lead.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="179002240146"></xptr>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>On Sunday morning, the 7th of March, about half past six, going to St. Martin's-lane, I saw the watchman the corner of Queen-street; passing by the house, this bundle lay by the side of the door; I took it up, and the man followed me, and took me.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17900424-23-verdict142" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17900424-23-verdict142" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17900424-23-punish143" type="punishmentDescription">
